Company Overview of Clearas Water Recovery, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Clearas Water Recovery, Inc. develops biological-based water treatment technologies for municipal and industrial point source dischargers. It provides Advanced Biological Nutrient Recovery system, a non-chemical treatment solution that uses microbiology–algae and other biological organisms to recover excess phosphorus, nitrogen, and other high-profile contaminants in industrial water discharge and wastewater effluent. Clearas Water Recovery, Inc. was formerly known as AlgEvolve Inc. and changed its name in July 2013. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Missoula, Montana.


